'''''Imfura''''', ni filime ngufi yo mu [[Rwanda|Rwanda yo muri]] 2017 iyobowe na Samuel Ishimwe ikaba yarayikoranye na Daniel Schweizer na Jean Perret kuri Haute École d'Art et de Design (HEAD) na Imitana Productions.<ref>https://africa.film/imfura-a-samuel-ishimwe-short-film/</ref> <ref>https://www.swissfilms.ch/en/person/samuel-ishimwe/A76E473A8D06475DA0944D06EB9622AB</ref>  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Moses Mwizerwa mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Kijyana Yves na Nyirababikira Hadidja mu nshingano zabo<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/imfura/</ref>.

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-43156718</ref>.  Bibaye umusaruro wambere wu [[Rwanda]] washyizwe mumarushanwa ya Berlinale Short. Muri make yatsindiye icyiciro cya silver Bear Jury Igiciro cya Berlin International Festival Festival<ref>https://www.hesge.ch/head/projet/film-imfura-samuel-ishimwe-remporte-prix-au-palm-springs-international-short-film-festival</ref> . 

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime ivuga ku nkuru yashyizwe mu [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Rwanda nyuma ya jenoside]] .<ref>https://africa.film/imfura-a-samuel-ishimwe-short-film/</ref> 

